headline: MCE Adds Ex-T-Mobile Executive Aleeta Willcuts to its Advisory Board to Help Redefine Telco Retail-Digital Customer Experience in U.S.
summary: SEATTLE, August 19, 2025--MCE Systems, the pioneer of digital-first mobile device lifecycle management (dDLM), today announced the appointment of Aleeta Willcuts, former Vice President of Retail Experience & Strategy at T-Mobile U.S., to its Board of Advisors. With more than 20 years of experience leading retail sales and operations, Aleeta will help accelerate MCE’s combined retail and digital transformation proposition to mobile operators.
